.TH APKW-UI 1 "April 2026" "APKW" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
apkw-ui \- GTK4 client for APK Workbench
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B apkw-ui
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B apkw-ui
opens the graphical APK Workbench client for project, toolchain, target, workflow, and
evidence management.
.PP
The UI expects the APK Workbench gRPC services to be available on the configured local
addresses. The packaged
.BR apkw (1)
launcher starts those services automatically before opening the UI.
.SH FILES
.TP
.I ~/.local/share/apkw/state/ui-config.json
Persisted UI configuration.
.TP
.I ~/.local/share/apkw/state/ui-state.json
Persisted UI state.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR apkw (1),
.BR apkw-cli (1)
